{"tid":971320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只要能打敗中共，台灣都可以係盟友，新加坡日韓都可以做朋友，唯美國馬首是瞻","createTime":"2019-01-06T14:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T07:58:31.000Z","uid":141151,"like":121,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e973fee37ca62bcd12387263536d46205e825bed","tid":971320,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:07:12.000Z","msg":"兩登/ PTT/ Reddit 周圍都有好多5毛內鬼<br />\n大家唔好被人分化<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>團結所有朋友/次要敵人，打擊主要敵人</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n就算要俾軍費美國駐兵，就算要俾利益日韓新，就算俾台仔笑，都要搞好大家關係，團結抗共<br />\n就算星仔成日想害香港，爭贏香港都唔緊要，打贏中共先再諗辦法追返<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>總之我唔會詆毀或者睇唔起潛在盟友</strong></span><br />\n係咁多"},{"pid":"a0f82d64218f11598752c1315466e5d787157822","tid":971320,"uid":40628,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:10:19.000Z","msg":"無錯，中共就挑起仇恨係起家"},{"pid":"241180508399507615c602262a1365563ab87782","tid":971320,"uid":161341,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:12:18.000Z","msg":"「最大敵人是支共」"},{"pid":"6f10d7a3f12dbdc5956753d781005a938502d10c","tid":971320,"uid":22566,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"a0f82d64218f11598752c1315466e5d787157822","tid":971320,"uid":40628,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:10:19.000Z","msg":"無錯，中共就挑起仇恨係起家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:12:42.000Z","msg":"然後趁亂執雞"},{"pid":"5a35701fd185239e8af89f26af6263a1fe3a8086","tid":971320,"uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"241180508399507615c602262a1365563ab87782","tid":971320,"uid":161341,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:12:18.000Z","msg":"「最大敵人是支共」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:15:09.000Z","msg":"目標明確，唔好被人分化"},{"pid":"8820d423975a812df654c8ca4c87e8d24861e773","tid":971320,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/